Say hello to clear, glowing skin with this refreshing Quench Kit for Oily Skin ✨

This kit is filled with Quench bestsellers that help control oil production, boost radiance and keep your skin fresh, clear and hydrated. 

Contents of the kit-

✨The Mama Cica Deep Pore Cleansing Micellar Water is a gentle cleansing formula packed with the goodness of cica and Korean ginseng along with calendula and lotus root. It removes deep-seated dirt, makeup and impurities, leaving behind skin that is clean and bright!

✨The Mama Cica Pore Clearing Exfoliating Face Wash is power-packed with deep cleansing ingredients like volcanic ash and adlay seed which help remove dirt, pollution and makeup from deep within. It exfoliates as it cleanses, leaving you with skin that is squeaky clean and soft! 

✨ The Mama Cica Rejuvenating Face Mist is Formulated using intensely hydrating cica and lotus root, this non-greasy, lightweight face mist instantly refreshes your skin and adds a radiant glow, it also contains niacinamide, a powerful yet gentle active that evens out your skin tone, while controlling sebum production.

✨Pamper your skin with Mon Cherry Sheet Mask that instantly boosts hydration, lightens dark spots and smoothens fine lines!
 

Great for travel and on-the-go skin glow, Quench Kit for Oily Skin fits perfectly in your bag and includes skin-loving essentials that keep your complexion spotless, smooth and dewy soft!

Includes a pretty pastel pouch to carry all your skincare essentials!

Retails for ₹599/-
